Language: uz

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:02.930
Github ning omboridagi rasmlarni 
ko‘rib chiqish orqali biz sizni 

00:00:02.930 --> 00:00:05.610
bu savollarga javob berishda bor 
imkoniyatingizni ishga solishingizni xohladik.

00:00:06.620 --> 00:00:09.620
Agar siz birinchi urinishdayoq bu javoblarni 
bilolmagan bo‘lsangiz, xavotirlanmang.

00:00:09.620 --> 00:00:12.520
Birinchidan, nima uchun ular drawable papkalar?

00:00:13.640 --> 00:00:17.173
Siz bizda drawable-mdpi , 
drawable-hdpi , drawable-xhdpi 

00:00:17.173 --> 00:00:22.380
va boshqa fayllar borligini payqagan bo‘lishingiz mumkin.

00:00:22.380 --> 00:00:24.610
Har bir fayl turli xil o‘lchamdagi 
qurilmalar uchun ko‘rsatadi.

00:00:26.110 --> 00:00:30.050
Yodda tuting, resolution - o‘lcham bo‘lib, 
ekranda qancha piksellar borligini bildiradi.

00:00:31.670 --> 00:00:35.310
Oldingi qurilmalarning ba’zilari 
bunchalik ko‘p pikselli emas edi.

00:00:35.310 --> 00:00:38.770
Yangi chiqayotgan qurilmalarning 
ekranida rasmlarni yanada 

00:00:38.770 --> 00:00:41.220
tiniqroq qilish uchun minglab piksellar bor. 

00:00:41.220 --> 00:00:45.690
Shuning uchun bu farqlarni to‘g‘irlash 
uchun bizda o‘rtacha zichlikdagi 

00:00:45.690 --> 00:00:51.310
qurilmalar uchun MDPI , yuqori zichlikdagi 
qurilmalar uchun esa HDPI , va hattoki 

00:00:52.420 --> 00:00:58.690
eng-eng-eng yuqori zichlikdagi 
qurilmalar uchun XXXHDPI fayllari bor.

00:00:58.690 --> 00:01:03.020
Ikkinchi savol: nima uchun bir xil 
rasmning ko‘plab versiyalari bor?

00:01:03.020 --> 00:01:05.459
Yaxshi, qurilmaning o‘lchamiga mos ravishda 

00:01:05.459 --> 00:01:09.110
biz mos Java fayldan rasmni ko‘rsatamiz.

00:01:09.110 --> 00:01:13.410
Bu yo‘l bilan rasm har doim 
tiniq va aniq ko‘rinadi.

00:01:13.410 --> 00:01:15.310
Sizda rasmlar nima uchun bu yo‘l 
bilan chizilganligi

00:01:15.310 --> 00:01:18.140
borasida ko‘plab javob berilmagan 
savollar borligiga ishonchim komil.

00:01:18.140 --> 00:01:19.340
Va bundan xavotir olmang.

00:01:19.340 --> 00:01:20.380
Buni kutgandik, albatta.

00:01:21.490 --> 00:01:24.570
Keyingi videoda biz bu savollarga javoblarni yana 
ham batafsilroq ko‘rib chiqamiz.

